  "description": "A nighttime photograph captures a vibrant cityscape with a spectacular fireworks display illuminating the sky. The fireworks burst in a complex pattern of gold, white, and red, contrasting against the deep blue of the night. Below the fireworks, a modern bridge spans a body of water, its lights creating a luminous path. In the background, a dense urban landscape rises, filled with illuminated buildings that form a golden, glowing horizon. The composition includes multiple bridges and a distant hilly shoreline. The scene evokes a sense of celebration and urban beauty.",
